---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Support — Walensis">
  <h1>Support</h1>
  <p>
    Need help with Walensis? Found a bug? Have a feature request? We'd love to
    hear from you.
  </p>

  <h2>Email</h2>
  <p>
    For all support questions, email
    <a href="mailto:support@walensis.com">support@walensis.com</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Reporting a problem</h2>
  <p>When reporting a bug, please include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>What you were doing when the problem happened</li>
    <li>Which marketplace and listing URL you were viewing</li>
    <li>What you expected to happen</li>
    <li>What actually happened (a screenshot helps)</li>
    <li>Your browser version (Chrome &gt; Help &gt; About Google Chrome)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Privacy questions</h2>
  <p>
    For questions about how we handle your data, see our
    <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> or email
    <a href="mailto:privacy@walensis.com">privacy@walensis.com</a>.
  </p>
</Layout>
